
# Keep the VSIX lean: exclude dev/test/artifacts and large copies.
# Keep branding assets explicitly included.
!assets/**
!assets/icon.png

# VS Code/editor/project metadata
.vscode/**
.github/**
**/.git/**
**/.github/**
**/.venv/**
**/.DS_Store

# Build/test artifacts
scripts/**
**/*.ts
**/*.map
**/*.log
**/*.bak
**/*.tmp
**/*~
coverage*/**
**/coverage/**
**/.coverage*
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc
node_modules/.cache/**
node_modules/**/README*
node_modules/**/Readme*
node_modules/**/CHANGELOG*
node_modules/**/changelog*
node_modules/**/HISTORY*
node_modules/**/MIGRATION*
node_modules/**/test/**
node_modules/**/tests/**
node_modules/**/bench.js
node_modules/**/.nycrc
node_modules/**/.eslintrc
node_modules/**/.npmignore
node_modules/**/tsconfig.json
node_modules/**/yarn.lock
node_modules/**/Makefile

# Packaged artifacts
**/*.vsix
**/*.zip

# Local inspection folders created during packaging
_extracted/**
_vsix_check/**
_tmp*/**
**/_tmp*/**

# This repo contains a nested copy of the full extension folder; exclude it
sona-ai-native-programming/**

# Docs not needed at runtime
PUBLISHER_UPDATE.md
EXTENSION_READY.md
icon.md

